<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idef780670-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s2222"><num value="2222">§ 2222.</num><heading> Details of law clerks</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Law clerks may be detailed by the Secretary of Agriculture for service in or out of Washington.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idef780671-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">(<ref href="/us/act/1911-03-04/ch238">Mar. 4, 1911, ch. 238</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/36/1236">36 Stat. 1236</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
